      "content": "Doha or Dubai seems like a solid backup. My main concern is that the terminal is absolute chaos right now because of the cancellations. It feels like no one knows what's going on and the logistics are just completely falling apart. If I try to rebook myself, what specific things should I look out for to avoid getting stuck in even more delays?",
